{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1c99276d09","title":"对赵朴初的《某公三哭》散曲的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ca7db8aef","index":0,"year":1965,"month":1,"day":31,"articleId":"1c99276d09"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"cce9cc2a23","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"1c99276d09","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"赵朴初，当时任中国佛教协会副会长兼秘书长、中国人民保卫世界和平委员会副主席。"},{"id":"56b3c6e2aa","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"1c99276d09","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"赵朴初写的散曲《某公三哭》指：一、哭西尼（1963年11月）；二、哭东尼（1964年5月）；三、哭自已（1964年11月）。发表在1965年2月1日《人民日报》。“某公”指赫鲁晓夫，“西尼”指肯尼迪，“东尼”指尼赫鲁。"},{"id":"e892e2d45f","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"1c99276d09","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央书记处书记、中央文教小组副组长康生1965年1月31日关于发表赵朴初写的《某公三哭》给毛泽东的报告上。报告说，赵朴初的《某公三哭》散曲已排出清样。如认为可以，拟在明天见报。请于今晚退姚漆同志办。"},{"id":"a862217a2c","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"1c99276d09","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"姚漆，当时任中共中央宣传部副部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"381f94c644","type":"title","text":"对赵朴初的《某公三哭》散曲的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"1c99276d09"},{"id":"cce9cc2a23","type":"paragraph","text":"很好。同意明天见报。送姚漆同志办理","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"1c99276d09"},{"id":"56b3c6e2aa","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"1c99276d09"},{"id":"e892e2d45f","type":"paragraph","text":"一月册一日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"1c99276d09"}],"page":{"id":"399d024e89","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"1c99276d09","start":471,"end":471}}}},"__N_SSG":true}